Height: 5' 11&quot;<br>
<br>
Hair\eye colour: White hair, green eyes<br>
<br>
Race: Drow<br>
<br>
Deity: Helos<br>
<br>
Personality/motivation: Always seen as a cool, calm collected individual, never panicking. He is quick, direct, to the point. He has a way with words, a way with speechcraft, he is very persuasive. He has the steadiest arm and quickest reactions in the land, which translates into his unparalled use of the bow. Known as the greatest sniper in the land, his skill with the bow and arrow is unmatched.<br>
<br>
Abilities: (3-5 max depending on amount of magic) he is not very magically orientated, although he does know one spell that gives him further and better vision. He is amazing with he bow, and very quick of pace.<br>
<br>
Single use/Limit break type ability: The Stinger - One time use arrow that when strikes, it calls forth a massive barrage of lightning towards the stricken one. <br>
<br>
Magic: None (partially lightning, read above)<br>
<br>
Magik: None (see above for spell)<br>
<br>
Weopon/s: Arcanis, an elvish longbow of great power (shoots thoise pointy things really hard<br>
<br>
History: Grew up in a small village near the Harvest Lands, at a young age he was noted to have superior levels of concentration. He was quickly outfitted with a bow by his grandfather, and with meticulous practice, his skills improved. He was part of the Drow Army, 4th battalion, at the age of 16 as a sniper, and diuring his 2 year long service, picked off over 170 enemy troops. He is renound across the land for his abilities, but has declined the honour of becoming a main officer in the army (fro reasons that are his own) and now works as a freelance adventurer.<br>
